Package com.microsoft.azure.datalake.store

Class OperationResponse

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.microsoft.azure.datalake.store.OperationResponse

  • public class OperationResponse
extends java.lang.Object
    information about a response from a server call. This class is a container for all the information from making a server call.

        time taken to get the token for this request, in nanoseconds. Should mostly be small.

      • responseContentLength

        public long responseContentLength
        Content-Length of the returned HTTP body (if return was not chunked). Callers should look at both this and responseChunked values to determine whether any data was returned by server.

      • responseChunked

        indicates whether HTTP body used chunked for Transfer-Encoding of the response
